        "cmip6.seaice.key_properties.overview": {
            "values": [
                "The sea ice model of MRI.COM is based on the Los Alamos sea ice model (CICE; Hunke and Lipscomb, 2010): thermodynamics of Mellor and Kantha (1989) with one-layer ice (Semtner, 1976); dynamics of the elastic-viscous-plastic rheology (Hunke and Dukowicz, 1997) and ridging scheme by Thorndike et al. (1975). Five thickness categories are allowed within a grid cell (Lipscomb, 2001). See Tsujino et al. (2017) for details."
            ]
        }, 
